partnerDetails.about: We supply a full range of Electrical and Lighting products On the ground floor, we run our retail division, which has an electrical counter & an impressive lighting display. Upstairs, we have our wholesale division & warehouse. We are proud to say that our wholesale division supplies a vast number of stores throughout KZN & beyond we are the supplier of choice for many contractors and project managers, also, our delivery service leads to total convenience for our customers.
